                <p/>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">Offrande </supplied> d'Alkiadas.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">Offering</supplied> of Alkiadas.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">Offerta</supplied> di Alkiadas.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
               <p>This vase was found in the fill below the altar bearing <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr114000</ref>. It is thus in clear relation with it.</p>
	           <p>The name should be that of the dedicant.</p>
	<p/>
